attachments.text: `<https://bitbucket.org/anyt-huh/heartbeat/commits/737e5e8f1911459d8c43df46c404f4b73f6f45a2|737e5e8>`  Make merge two requirement.txt django's requirement and grpc's requirement - Jong Hun Oh
`<https://bitbucket.org/anyt-huh/heartbeat/commits/1dcf31c02e0b5044ce7c695873747fd24f06c476|1dcf31c>`  Fix permission bug, implement token loading - Jeong Woon Choi

• Solve concurrency issues, merge disk and raid info together

     In java running threads is started by start() method and not run() method.
     Also I changed protobuf files so that DiskUsage includes raid data because
     I find it redundant to just seperate raid info.
• Implement SystemInfoWriter (partial)
• Implement missing functions in SystemInfoWriter
• Add log folder to gitignore
• Improvement: More secure data file writing

     Now the files and folders created by SystemInfoWriter have strict
     permissions. Also files are all created under log directory.
